============================
file transformation toolbox
============================
Time-stamp: <2013-01-09 Xiaoqin Yang>


Usage of bed_divide.py
=======================

In bed file, reads were first divided by positive and negative strand, 
then by chromosomes. Two folders, each of them have 24 bed files.

python bed_divide.py -i xxx.bed


Usage of wig_divide.py
=======================

wig file were divided into 24 wig files according to chromosomes.

python wig_divide.py -i xxx.wig


Usage of bed_to_wig.py
=======================

transfer bed file into wig file.

python bed_to_wig.py -i input bed file -o output wig file